name: $include
desc: The name of a resource to not include in a selection.

name: $exclude
desc: A reference to the response resource to the original processing of a resource.

name: $origresponse
desc: A reference value which must be quoted to authorize an action.

name: $reference
desc: The sequence number associated with an item for reprocessing.

name: $item
desc: The reference period for the action being requested.

name: $period
desc: The processing status from a check on the processing status of a resource such as the adjudication of a claim.
